name: Grid
text:
Display horizontal or vertical grid lines at locations
given by a supplied Ticker.

attrs.name: band_fill_alpha
descs: property type: NumberSpec
The fill alpha of alternating bands between Grid lines.

attrs.name: band_fill_color
descs: property type: ColorSpec
The fill color of alternating bands between Grid lines.

attrs.name: bounds
descs: property type: Either ( Auto , Tuple ( Float , Float  ) )

Bounds for the rendered grid lines. If unset, the grid
lines will span the entire plot in the given dimension.

attrs.name: dimension
descs: property type: Int

Which dimension the Axis Grid lines will intersect. The
x-axis is dimension 0 (vertical Grid lines) and the y-axis
is dimension 1 (horizontal Grid lines).

attrs.name: grid_line_alpha
descs: property type: NumberSpec
The line alpha of the Grid lines.

attrs.name: grid_line_cap
descs: property type: Enum ( LineCap  )
The line cap of the Grid lines.

attrs.name: grid_line_color
descs: property type: ColorSpec
The line color of the Grid lines.

attrs.name: grid_line_dash
descs: property type: DashPattern
The line dash of the Grid lines.

attrs.name: grid_line_dash_offset
descs: property type: Int
The line dash offset of the Grid lines.

attrs.name: grid_line_join
descs: property type: Enum ( LineJoin  )
The line join of the Grid lines.

attrs.name: grid_line_width
descs: property type: NumberSpec
The line width of the Grid lines.

attrs.name: minor_grid_line_alpha
descs: property type: NumberSpec
The line alpha of the minor Grid lines.

attrs.name: minor_grid_line_cap
descs: property type: Enum ( LineCap  )
The line cap of the minor Grid lines.

attrs.name: minor_grid_line_color
descs: property type: ColorSpec
The line color of the minor Grid lines.

attrs.name: minor_grid_line_dash
descs: property type: DashPattern
The line dash of the minor Grid lines.

attrs.name: minor_grid_line_dash_offset
descs: property type: Int
The line dash offset of the minor Grid lines.

attrs.name: minor_grid_line_join
descs: property type: Enum ( LineJoin  )
The line join of the minor Grid lines.

attrs.name: minor_grid_line_width
descs: property type: NumberSpec
The line width of the minor Grid lines.

attrs.name: ticker
descs: property type: Instance ( Ticker  )
The Ticker to use for computing locations for the Grid lines.

attrs.name: x_range_name
descs: property type: String

A particular (named) x-range to use for computing screen
locations when rendering a grid on the plot. If unset, use the
default x-range.

attrs.name: y_range_name
descs: property type: String

A particular (named) y-range to use for computing screen
locations when rendering a grid on the plot. If unset, use the
default y-range.
